,” says\nMa.\nKeya\nis sad. It's time to go back to the burrow.","words":[[200,"“It"],[201,"looks"],[202,"like"],[203,"we"],[204,"are"],[205,"closer"],[206,"to"],[207,"the"],[208,"water"],[209,"now,"],[210,"Ma,”"],[211,"says"],[212,"Keya."],[213,"“Eeeyyy!"],[214,"The"],[215,"sea"],[216,"is"],[217,"coming"],[218,"in"],[219,"and"],[220,"it"],[221,"will"],[222,"soon"],[223,"gobble"],[224,"up"],[225,"the"],[226,"beach,”"],[227,"says"],[228,"Ma."],[229,"Keya"],[230,"is"],[231,"sad."],[232,"It's"],[233,"time"],[234,"to"],[235,"go"],[236,"back"],[237,"to"],[238,"the"],[239,"burrow."]]},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/53600/size6/9af70a01d578bf2fa03645205ed6b648.jpg","text":"“It’s\nsuch a big, big world outside,” thinks Keya. “I can’t wait to\ngo out again tomorrow!”\nKeya\nslowly falls asleep, her ten legs tired from all the marching.\nShe\ndreams of visiting the beach again. \nLeft, right, left!","words":[[240,"“It’s"],[241,"such"],[242,"a"],[243,"big,"],[244,"big"],[245,"world"],[246,"outside,”"],[247,"thinks"],[248,"Keya."],[249,"“I"],[250,"can’t"],[251,"wait"],[252,"to"],[253,"go"],[254,"out"],[255,"again"],[256,"tomorrow!”"],[257,"Keya"],[258,"slowly"],[259,"falls"],[260,"asleep,"],[261,"her"],[262,"ten"],[263,"legs"],[264,"tired"],[265,"from"],[266,"all"],[267,"the"],[268,"marching."],[269,"She"],[270,"dreams"],[271,"of"],[272,"visiting"],[273,"the"],[274,"beach"],[275,"again."],[276,"Left,"],[277,"right,"],[278,"left!"]]},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/53599/size6/1178a561346b9d6d27079b500c9f5a8b.jpg","text":"Left,\nright, left… on the sand.\nLeft,\nright, left… in the waves.\nLeft,\nright, left… \nKeya marches on in her sleep.","words":[[279,"Left,"],[280,"right,"],[281,"left…"],[282,"on"],[283,"the"],[284,"sand."],[285,"Left,"],[286,"right,"],[287,"left…"],[288,"in"],[289,"the"],[290,"waves."],[291,"Left,"],[292,"right,"],[293,"left…"],[294,"Keya"],[295,"marches"],[296,"on"],[297,"in"],[298,"her"],[299,"sleep."]]},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/53586/size6/a8b6e2f3b6e177589243805bc420ad70.jpg","text":"A\nCast of Crabs\nLet’s\nhead to the beach and meet Keya and her crab friends. Most crabs walk\nand swim sideways. Did you know that a group of crabs is called a CAST?\nSoldier Crabs: Thousands\nof Soldier Crabs live together at the edge of mangroves near beaches.\nThey are small and are easy prey for shorebirds. They sift for food\nin the sand and whatever they don’t eat, they roll into tiny balls\nand throw away!\nGhost Crabs: Because\ntheir eyes are on stalks, Ghost Crabs can see all around. But they\ncan’t see what’s on top of their heads! They are one of the\nfastest runners on the planet. They are the colour of the sand, and\nyou can barely see them as they dart across the beach.","words":[[300,"A"],[301,"Cast"],[302,"of"],[303,"Crabs"],[304,"Let’s"],[305,"head"],[306,"to"],[307,"the"],[308,"beach"],[309,"and"],[310,"meet"],[311,"Keya"],[312,"and"],[313,"her"],[314,"crab"],[315,"friends."],[316,"Most"],[317,"crabs"],[318,"walk"],[319,"and"],[320,"swim"],[321,"sideways."],[322,"Did"],[323,"you"],[324,"know"],[325,"that"],[326,"a"],[327,"group"],[328,"of"],[329,"crabs"],[330,"is"],[331,"called"],[332,"a"],[333,"CAST"],[334,"?"],[335,"Soldier"],[336,"Crabs:"],[337,"Thousands"],[338,"of"],[339,"Soldier"],[340,"Crabs"],[341,"live"],[342,"together"],[343,"at"],[344,"the"],[345,"edge"],[346,"of"],[347,"mangroves"],[348,"near"],[349,"beaches."],[350,"They"],[351,"are"],[352,"small"],[353,"and"],[354,"are"],[355,"easy"],[356,"prey"],[357,"for"],[358,"shorebirds."],[359,"They"],[360,"sift"],[361,"for"],[362,"food"],[363,"in"],[364,"the"],[365,"sand"],[366,"and"],[367,"whatever"],[368,"they"],[369,"don’t"],[370,"eat,"],[371,"they"],[372,"roll"],[373,"into"],[374,"tiny"],[375,"balls"],[376,"and"],[377,"throw"],[378,"away!"],[379,"Ghost"],[380,"Crabs:"],[381,"B